Montana Territory (1873-02-17)

1873/02/17 -> 1889/11/07

Montana Territory gained the small remnant of Dakota Territory that remained between Montana and Wyoming Territories.

(U.S. Stat., vol. 17, ch. 147 [1873]/p. 464; Van Zandt, 136, 145, 150)
